name: ERROR-0.2 | Play With Me
description:
Too many mistakes are being made. Too many failures will come. There's no time to take a hand. There's still time left for us, don't go down, get out, play with me, don't let yourself down.
ERRORS- A convergence of illustrations and glitches.
